      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in superlative condition, reflecting a rigorous maintenance history and an uncompromising standard of care. From the pristine cabin environment to the flawless mechanical synchronization, every detail satisfies the requirements of the most discerning collector. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
