    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age, maintained in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Every body panel alignment is laser-straight. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, the dashboard is free of UV damage, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. All electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function with factory-new precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records, showcasing preventative maintenance that exceeds manufacturer recommendations. The engine bay is pristine, the undercarriage is free of corrosion, and the transmission shifts with seamless fluidity. This is an investment-grade example intended for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
