      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated BMW engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been meticulously overhauled for optimal cam timing. The power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring maximum traction. This example features a reinforced rear subframe to address chassis fatigue, a common weak point, ensuring structural rigidity. With factory-spec compression across all cylinders and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation, this is a collector-grade specimen built for the technical purist.",
